divs: Sighting DetailsCar accident on the road.I stopped to snap a picture. I came back to the house and was looking over the photo after showing it to my folks. The first shot shows nothing unusual. but then above the tree line a minute later close to the wire it caught the object. circular in shape. Apon closer exam I found what looks like a grey bottom and a disturbance around the object.
